Phase 0: Just play a lot of Hanabi with friends and boost my curiosity\
Phase 1: Implement game mechanics (initial version) - Finished December 2021\
Phase 2: Literature study/ create work plan and sketches of further work\
Phase 3: Write code for ETL-flow\
Phase 4: Implement basic machine learning models - several if possible?\
